Entries.default: "Sh-sh-shining God light your path, stranger! Can I interest you in any of our wares?"

"Used to work a farm, growing vorlas. N-n-never thought I'd get out of there. 

"Erm. Sorry. Would you like to buy something?"
"We g-g-gathered what we could. Much of our coin goes toward feeding those in need, over at the temple."
